{
  "stem": "24364.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then they wanted to ship us back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "A couple of times they wanted to ship us back because there was not enough money to pay for the accommodations.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so it-- it wasn't a very pleasant time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "However, I have to add that some of the Bratislava Jews were extremely nice to us and really as helpful as could be.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "At that time, they were still living, you know, normally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was no problem in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Problems began later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I myself was invited by perfect strangers to stay with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I stayed with one family for four weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I stayed with another family for two weeks, and, you know, in relative luxury.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And that was a very pleasant change from the [NON-ENGLISH] In this respect, I was pretty lucky.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well originally, as I said, the first month or so we could not leave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then eventually, yes, they gave us permission.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Originally they gave us permission to leave for a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on-- I think the people paid for us, when-- you know, they gave them some money, in order to get us out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not 100% sure of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But somehow I have the feeling that they had to pay some money to get us out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And actually the people I stayed with were really quite rich.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I'm sure that-- I don't know how much they have to pay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm sure they must have had to pay something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I guess they could well afford it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were really super nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we, we got permission.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We got a permission slip.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anytime we could leave the [NON-ENGLISH], we had to leave with some sort of permission slip.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they handed them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "At the-- not at the beginning, but eventually, relatively freely.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
